      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Vougioukas et al. [CITATION_1] introduce a backscatter transmitter circuit based on the Arduino development board, which uses a bit vector to form a packet consisting of 8-byte preamble, 4byte sync, and 6-byte data."
